item.title: What's New
item.description: I, Arduino A Maker’s Coffee Table Eyantra Finals 6 DOF Servo Arm HNH Robo Kit EYRC-BOT in Action 2020 Highlights 6 DOF Servo Arm Alright, We have got our Servo Arm fixed. Last time we used only arduino to control the arm for pre-loaded movement. Well, This time I am thinking of intergrating ROS with it and use Moveit! to plan a path for the end effector to Go to a certain Pose provided by us.
